## Dependency Management

- Check peer dependency compatibility BEFORE installing
- Lock dependency versions — use exact versions (no `^` or `~`)
- Run `npm audit` after every dependency change
- Never install from untrusted sources
- Document WHY each dependency is needed

### Dependency Audit Checklist

1. Is this package actively maintained? (last commit < 6 months)
2. Known critical vulnerabilities?
3. Bundle size acceptable?
4. Duplicates existing dependency functionality?
5. Lighter alternative available?

